AMALUNGU ePhalamende avumelene ngokuthi azozidingida izinkinga zeSABC ezimayelana nokudilizwa kwabantu. USomlomo, uNksz Thandi Modise, uvumile ukuthi kube nenkuluÂ­mompikiswano ngesonto elizayo ngemva kokuba i-IFP ifake isicelo sokuba lubhekwe udaba. UNobhala wePhalamende, uMnuz Masibulele Xaso, utshele ikomiti lezinhlelo ukuthi kuzokhulunywa ngodaba ngoLwesibili. I-SABC yayithe ifuna ukudiliza abasebenzi abawu-400 ukuze yonge imali. Abezinyunyana namaqembu aphikisayo bathi kumele kutholakale ezinye izindlela zokonga kodwa kungaxoshwa abasebenzi. Abamaqembu ezepolitiki bathe uhulumeni akangenelele I-SABC isizihlehlisile izinhlelo zokudiliza kuze kube sekupheleni kukaDisemba.